<div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"><br />A human starts as 19 ellipsoids: head, upper torso, lower torso, and 4 limbs. Each limb is the upper limb, lower limb, palm/sole, and a set of fingers/toes. Animate that framework and render it, and it'll look roughly like the characters from the fighting game Ballz 3D. A bit more tweaking of each ellipsoid, and you have something over which to draw a sprite sheet.<br /></div><br />It sounds so easy that way... but in fact it's probably not as simple heh. Do you really have experience in this ?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Tue Jan 05, 2010 2:31 pm</p><hr />
